{"tid":1613764,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［黨鐵奇聞］旺角站上車，下一個站旺角站","createTime":"2019-10-02T15:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:44:38.000Z","uid":280223,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3379ef3e4086b4f5b68f9ea8dac887a7c90e7120","tid":1613764,"uid":280223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:27:03.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇ching同我一樣遇過呢個經歷<br />\n<br />\n今日2230左右同fd傾完計落旺角站搭黨鐵（冇任何封站）<br />\n上車果陣都有望一望塊牌，往荃灣方向<br />\n搭緊時候冇留意擴播，但開車門果刻係旺角個月台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行出車門睇條線，變左往黃埔方向！<br />\n<br />\n即係變左太子站搭落黎，但我同fd再確認多次，<br />\n佢見我係行落去旺角站<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（因為佢旺角搭小巴）<br />\n我望其他人唔覺佢地有異樣<br />\n有冇人同我有同樣經歷？ <br />\n抑或831之後，太子站時不時會有野發生？"},{"pid":"8488dbed9d9942d7a0b78848c004533da580ad48","tid":1613764,"uid":9769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TEyU8o8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTEyU8o8.jpg&h=d567dc94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"944b7a35ba5ec3a3ea6eab14a5dca8e2bbfce16a","tid":1613764,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:44:38.000Z","msg":"巴打最近精神如何"}]}